name: ᴍᴀᴀɴꜱɪ ᴊᴀɪɴ "ᴄᴏɴᴛᴇᴍᴘʟᴀᴛɪɴɢ ᴇᴅɢᴇꜱ ᴏꜰ ɪɴᴛᴇʟʟɪɢɪʙɪʟɪᴛʏ ᴜᴘᴏɴ ᴀ ᴍɪʟʟᴇɴɪᴀʟ ᴘɪɴᴋ ᴘᴏᴜꜰ (ʀᴇᴄᴇɴᴛ ᴍᴏᴛɪꜰ)" (2022)
description: maansi jain's first 3d scan in lisbon, portugal starring the artist upon found concrete in a millennial pink hue (scanning assistance by nina pertsov). in this work the 3d scanner app is engaged as a tool of documentation, while examining the human effort required on either side of the interaction with the documentary tool of a 3d scanner. the artist attempted to create an intelligible image through 3-d scanning to test a more modern light writing technique than analog and digital photography are anymore...
